[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "……で、事情は分かったけど、\nどうして私まで素材集めに呼ばれたの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00249",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "え、クレオも待ってるだけって暇かなーって。\n外に出るの、いい気晴らしになるでしょ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00250",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "ありがとう。体動かしたいって思ってたんだ。\n……あ、今クレオって呼んだ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00251",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "うん。この前自分から呼び捨てにしてって\n言ってたじゃん",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00252",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "言った！　ふふ、呼び捨てはあまりされないから、\nなんだかくすぐったくて、嬉しい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00253",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "王女様を呼び捨てなんて……！　アルビーナったら、\nずっと寝てないから判断が鈍っちゃったのかしら",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00254",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "王女様とも距離を縮めてしまえるなんて……\n姉様、やはりただ者じゃない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00255",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ベーップ！　アタシを盛り立てるためとはいえ、\n最近ちょっとほめすぎ！　背中がむず痒いわい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00256",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "とはいえ、アルビちゃんはほめられたいので、\n適度にはよろしく",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00257",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "アルビーナ以外のみんなも、\n呼び捨てにしてくれていいよ？　ふふ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00258",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "……クレオ、この間よりちょっと元気になった？\nカフェで美味しいもの、いっぱい食べられた？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00259",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "うん。おかげで戦う準備はいつでもできてる。\nあなたも――アルビーナも、あいつらと戦うの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00260",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "戦うよ！　もちろん、クレオの邪魔はしない。\nアタシにできることで援護させていただきやすよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00261",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "力じゃかなわないから、その分頭を使ってね！\n一般人が九偉人様にどこまでやれるか、楽しみでしょ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00262",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "一応クレオ姫を立ててはいるけれど、\n野心が顔と言葉に出てるわね……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00263",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "１日で新境地に達したくらいだし、\n天下を取れる素質はあるわ……。……ん、この気配",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00264",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "みんな、魔物よ！　警戒して",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00265",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "ちょうど戦いたかったんだよね。\nここは私に任せてくれない？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00266",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "はあーーーっ！！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00267",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "おおー……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00268",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "すごいわ。力強く、洗練された身のこなし……\nつい見惚れちゃったわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00269",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "ありがとう！\n神聖国の聖戦士にそう言ってもらえるなんて光栄だね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00270",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "いやほんと、おみそれしました。\n強い。ヘルトに負けたのが不思議なぐらい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00271",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "あいつら、まぁとんでもなかったからね。\nもう、次は負けないんだからっ！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00272",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "うん、クレオの力にアタシの新しい力を\n組み合わせたら、ほんとにいけるかも",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00273",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "……って、そうじゃなくてもレスナたちが\n勝ってくれるよね。でも念には念を入れよってことで",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00274",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "よし、まずは新装備の調合、張り切っていこう！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00275",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]